HEADWORD: Staphyloma
<hw>Staph`y*lo"ma</hw> <pr>(-l⟦omac⟧"m⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L., fr. Gr. <grk>stafy`lwma</grk>, from <grk>stafylh`</grk> a
